Insider Threat Matrix™ Attribution
==================================

This project maps OSINT articles to techniques from the Insider Threat Matrix™
(ITM), an open investigative framework published at:

  https://insiderthreatmatrix.org/

Canonical machine-readable taxonomy:

  https://github.com/forscie/insider-threat-matrix

The slim index shipped in shared/data/itm_index.json is derived from that
upstream JSON (Apache License 2.0). Refresh with:

  python -m apps.aggregator refresh_itm

